&lt;p&gt;The Support organization at GitHub is looking for an experienced leader for our Developer Support team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Developer Support team is responsible for delivering world class support to GitHub.com customers. The team aims to solve customer problems, be voice of the customer, and delight customers every step of the way. As leader of that group, the right candidate will be responsible for developing a strategic vision, the team’s roadmap, and for delivering results. This candidate will be responsible for thought leadership, mentorship, and act as an advocate for both the team and GitHub’s customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Customer Success organization is highly distributed and the right candidate can thrive in an environment of asynchronous communication. We expect that you will create working relationships with coworkers and peers in locations around the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
