&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and deliver a healthy and sustainable support strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refine and build empowering processes that delight customers and employees&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work and communicate cross-functionally, advocating for the needs and voice of support&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influence overall product decisions using customer feedback and support data metrics&lt;/li&gt;
