&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We are looking to hire a Director to lead the growing Strategic Finance team at GitHub. The successful candidate will regularly interface with our Executive Team to create plans, derive company-wide goals, and collaborate effectively with cross-functional teams to drive successful outcomes. We’re looking for an organized thinker who can drive multiple high-priority projects simultaneously while inspiring and growing a team of high potential managers and analysts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Building. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Continuously challenge each member of the team to deliver their best work. Identify top priority opportunities for the team and instill a growth mindset across the team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Financial Planning &amp;amp; Analysis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;. Own and develop the wholistic financial trajectory of the business. Work with department leaders across functional groups to responsibly instrument and guide the business. Identify key metrics and evaluate how effectively resources are deployed against those metrics, driving accountability across the company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Communication. &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Oversee the company’s financial plan and drive monthly reporting packages. Surface and deconstruct performance of key financial and operational metrics to our senior leadership team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Iterating &amp;amp; Forecasting.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Embrace new information and proactively look for ways to improve understanding of our business performance. Utilize new information to help the team improve visibility and forecasting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Education. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s degree.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Experience.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; 6+ years of relevant work experience, foundational work preferably at a leading investment bank, Venture Capital / Private Equity firm, with experience at a fast growing SaaS business. Public company experience is a plus.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Management Experience. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;2+ years of experience managing a team. Track record of successful leadership and team-building.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Experience.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Extensive competency in building and auditing sophisticated financial models and large data sets.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Intuition. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;SaaS experience strongly preferred but not required. Deep understanding of the key drivers of a SaaS business is essential.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Self Starter Mentality&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;. Proactive thinker determined to build processes that scale and provide a solid foundation for long term growth.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication Skills. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Distill and simplify complex financial concepts for all audiences.  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interpersonal Skills.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Build trust and effectively collaborate cross-functionally. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
