&lt;p&gt;GitHub is looking for a talented engineer to join Git Ecosystem team, working primarily on VFS for Git, Git LFS and other file storage features. The ideal candidate will be passionate about improving the Git experience for developers that work with repositories with extreme amounts of files or very large files.&lt;/p&gt;
