&lt;p&gt;GitHub is looking for a talented engineer to join our Git Infrastructure team. You will focus on the systems and tools that enable our engineers to operate and scale the world&#39;s largest code hosting platform. More specifically, you will develop, automate, test, monitor, and maintain the Git repository storage infrastructure that forms the core of GitHub&#39;s product offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Git Infrastructure team is highly distributed and the right candidate will thrive in an environment of asynchronous communication. We expect you to have strong written communication skills and be able to create working relationships with coworkers in locations around the globe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Git Infrastructure engineer at GitHub you&#39;ll always be challenged to solve interesting and novel problems that have real impact on how the world builds software.&lt;/p&gt;
