&lt;div&gt;At GitHub, we strive to be the place where developers and enterprises trust us to be the place to create and consume open source software. GitHub is the home to 31 million developers and countless enterprises and that trust must be earned day-in and day-out. Product Management is core to developing, earning and keeping that trust. Product Management is above all tasked with listening to customers, talking to them and understanding the problems they&#39;re trying to solve. In concert with our GitHub&#39;s Engineering and Design teams, we work together to prioritize the biggest impact problems for our customers.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;GitHub Platform is looking for a Senior Product Mangaer to join our Ecosystem team. The Ecosystem team work on the APIs, API authorization, billing tools, Marketplace, and integrations at GitHub. These empower developers and organizations to integrate their products and build their businesses on GitHub.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Our team members span a variety of timezones, genders, races, cultures, disability statuses, sexual orientations, family responsibilities, experience levels, professional backgrounds, personality types, and more. You&#39;re expected to have strong written communication skills and to excel in working relationships with people different than you.&lt;/div&gt;
