&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in one or more major programming languages -- you&#39;ll need to build a demo or proof of concept for various stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Built an integration with GitHub&#39;s API.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
