&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience working across organizations with Sales, Marketing, Support, Product, Engineering and Design. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
