&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years experience working on continuous integration projects/services with at-scale experience or similar experience around commercial software delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years experience working on an application team, preferably on the frontend of a web application&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Impactful, direct experience implementing development tools for very large or fast-growing teams of developers. We&#39;re looking for projects like:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Development on projects with Primer, Bootstrap, or similar frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Development on API projects using nodeJS and/or GraphQL&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
