&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with nodejs &amp;amp; primer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years working on UX and Usability projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ChatOps development/automation (Hubot/Probot)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Additional experience nice to have:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work on Projects that use Docker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working on design UX for web applications and workflows&lt;/li&gt;
