&lt;p&gt;The Professional Services team at GitHub focuses on helping our customers improve the lives of developers working on the GitHub platform. As a Services Account Engineer you will directly impact the lives of developers by working with some of the largest software companies on earth by crafting many aspects of software delivery. You will help our customers plan, prioritize, launch, and accelerate their initiatives in building on GitHub.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will succeed in this role if you are a highly technical individual who feels as comfortable working with tech leaders to map out software delivery initiative roadmaps as you do writing code. You will work with customers from the planning phase through maintaining the system. You will be their primary technical contact at GitHub and establish relationships with admins and their tech leaders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;user-content-as-a-services-account-engineer-you-will&quot; class=&quot;anchor&quot; href=&quot;https://github.com/github/services/blob/master/engineering/docs/hiring-and-onboarding/job-posting-resources/services-account-engineer-apac.md#as-a-services-account-engineer-you-will&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help transform software delivery at some of the largest software organizations through hands-on assistance&lt;/li&gt;
