&lt;p&gt;To succeed in this role you will need to be based in Australia. You will spend up to 50% of your time traveling. Because of our travel requirements you should live within a reasonable distance to an airport in Australia. In addition to remotely working with the team on project and customer priorities, you will be working both locally onsite and remotely with customers in the Australia and Asia/Pacific region.&lt;/p&gt;
