&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build high-volume event collection, processing and storage systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with application engineers to build product features that use GitHub&#39;s data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with teammates to design data pipelines and APIs, seeking and offering feedback along the way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop foundational data infrastructure, enabling other teams to build data-centric features&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work across many languages including Go, Java, Ruby and Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Share responsibility for the availability and performance of our team&#39;s systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
