&lt;p&gt;GitHub is changing the way the world builds software and we want you to help change the way we build GitHub. We&#39;re looking for an engineer to work with a dynamic and distributed group of engineers building and improving our platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We empower developers and organizations to integrate their products and build their businesses on the GitHub Platform. Help us develop the workflows, tools, payment solutions and APIs to build and run GitHub Apps and OAuth Apps so that our integrators can realize their full potential on our platform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The GitHub Ecosystem team is highly distributed. You should thrive in an environment of asynchronous communication. We expect you to have strong written and verbal communication skills and be able to build working relationships with coworkers in locations around the globe. As an Ecosystem Engineer, you&#39;ll always be challenged to solve unique and interesting problems that have a real impact on how your co-workers and GitHub integrators build software.&lt;/p&gt;
