&lt;li&gt;Ensuring consistency in candidate process, in compliance with any EEO/OFCCP guidelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advocates for and delivers a fantastic candidate experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sourcing of quality candidates for niche or hard-to-fill roles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Minimum Qualifications:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least three years of solid experience recruiting full-time, technical and sales employees within an organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have a minimum of two years of corporate recruiting experience within a technology based company &lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working within an ATS (Applicant Tracking System)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience partnering with hiring managers, leaders, or other employees outside of the hiring space&lt;/li&gt;
