&lt;p&gt;GitHub is looking for a Web Designer to join our Site Design team. The site design team designs and maintains all of our non-product websites, for example GitHub&#39;s marketing site, event sites, annual reports, brand campaigns, and more. As a Web Designer, you’ll work closely with other designers, project managers, engineers, and our marketing team to translate ideas into beautiful and effective websites.&lt;/p&gt;
