&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to translate business goals into user-facing websites, from early design exploration to front-end development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in design and code reviews with your teammates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with our creative team to give life to the GitHub brand on the web.&lt;/li&gt;
